title: [QUESTION] Trying to build SkiaSharp from sources
body:
Hello.
Please help, i trying to build SkiaSharp from sources. 

I download zip archive from github , 
write this command:  .\bootstrapper.ps1 -t externals-download
And open project  source\SkiaSharpSource.sln
But Visual Studio failed with build and  show's me this picture:
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/32514002/129036807-301bf1f4-572d-4acd-8304-2105ddecefba.png)

What means this Yellow warning triangles? How to resolve this?
